# Fireshit Capture Immunity License
## Version 0.1

Copyright © 2026 Giz@SUBSTR8Games. All rights reserved.

### 0. Purpose and Status

The Fireshit Capture Immunity License exists to permit inspection, local execution, modification, compilation, community development, and independent interoperability while preventing proprietary capture of the Fireshit software suite.

This is a source-available license. It is not an open-source license and must not be represented as one.

No rights are granted except those expressly stated in this License.

### 1. Definitions

**Licensor** means Giz@SUBSTR8Games and any successor copyright holder expressly identified in the Covered Software.

**You** means the individual or legal entity exercising permissions granted by this License.

**Covered Software** means the first-party Fireshit source code, executable code, build material, documentation, and other files expressly distributed under this License. It excludes material carrying a separate valid third-party or file-specific license notice.

**Modified Version** means any work that copies, changes, translates, adapts, incorporates, or is derived from any copyrightable portion of the Covered Software.

**Corresponding Source** means the preferred form for modifying a distributed version of the Covered Software, including its source code, build definitions, installation material, and modifications necessary to reproduce that version.

**Independent Work** means software that communicates or interoperates with the Covered Software without copying or incorporating any copyrightable portion of it.

**Third Party** means any person or entity other than you, your employees, and contractors operating exclusively on your behalf and under your control.

**Capture** means any activity prohibited by Section 4.

